OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of patchy rain will
OL,6,Fsink south across Wales on Monday,
OL,7,Fclearing to sunny spells during the
OL,8,Fafternoon with a northerly breeze
OL,9,Fslowly increasing. Feeling rather
OL,10,Fchilly for the time of year, despite
OL,11,Fthe sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry overnight with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud and lengthy clear
OL,15,Fspells developing with a risk of a
OL,16,Frural frost in the east. Turning
OL,17,Fcloudier from the northwest towards
OL,18,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
