OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,6,Farriving across Wales during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Turning drier and brighter
OL,8,Finto the afternoon with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Perhaps the odd isolated
OL,10,Fshower in the north later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FBlustery with sunny spells and heavy
OL,14,Fshowers on both Wednesday and
OL,15,FThursday. More settled on Friday with
OL,16,Fdrier and brighter conditions.
OL,17,FRemaining chilly, with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
